@node WORLD "What's The World?"
The World is a database that contains information about every county on
Earth, e.g. capital, size, population, languages, religions, currency,
GNP, national holiday, Head of Government, Cheif of State, climate, 
natural resources and independence. 
The World is easy to handle, just press the buttons.
@endnode
