@node TRANSLATE "Translation"
If you want The World to be in your language you just translate
'translation.text' and send it to me. But please contact me BEFORE
sending any translation. This will save you from translating 
everything to a language, that The World already are translated to.

If you are the first one that creates a translation into a language,
you will get the full functional version whitout payment. If you
have already payed you will get your money back.
@endnode
